longBusinessSummary: EyeCity.com, Inc. operates as a natural resource exploration company. It purchases rights to small scale mining concessions with the intent on developing and assessing the extent of mineralization in the concession areas. The company was incorporated in 1977 and is based in Lake Mary, Florida.
